{"tid":1261997,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4/Xbox One/PC]《賽博朋克2077》PS4版容量為80GB Xbox One X版支持4K","createTime":"2019-06-27T13:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T15:18:32.000Z","uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dde82d16bc2fd01774a4313abdf0d6543515a92d","tid":1261997,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:13:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2367922946811546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2367922946811546&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0djWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=86843157\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2367922946811546</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qorJFrJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqorJFrJ.jpg&h=0267f511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Multi】《賽博朋克2077》PS4版容量為80GB Xbox One X版支持4K<br />\n<br />\n  開發商CDPR製作的遊戲體積都挺大，《賽博朋克2077》（Cyberpunk 2077）也不例外。近日CDPR宣布《賽博朋克2077》PS4版容量大小為80GB，這可比《往日不再》容量還多13GB。硬盤吃緊的玩家如果想玩《賽博朋克2077》，可能需要刪些遊戲了。<br />\n<br />\n  《賽博朋克2077》主要劇情在夜之城進行，這意味著有大量建築物、NPC、任務、車輛及其他物品需要加載渲染，這對主機硬件要求比較高了。玩家如果擁有Xbox One X主機，則能以4K分辨率進入絢麗的遊戲世界遊玩，但目前不清楚Xbox One版需要多少GB的硬盤空間。<br />\n<br />\n  《賽博朋克2077》容量大小也比《巫師3》大了很多，後者PC版安裝好所有補丁和DLC，也只需49.1GB硬盤空間。考慮到《巫師3》內容已經相當豐富，那《賽博朋克2077》會更加精彩？<br />\n<br />\n  《賽博朋克2077》將於2020年4月16日在PS4/Xbox One和PC平台上發售，目前已開啟預售。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RBB9AZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRBB9AZ4.jpg&h=56f6390f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EoAFHE5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEoAFHE5.jpg&h=f8595619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n<strong><ins>[HEHE]《賽博朋克 2077 (Cyberpunk 2077)》的曖昧對像不會再局限於異性</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1259368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1259368/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6a068caa3f9d99bfd3497ae8e6be0276fa3659a2","tid":1261997,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5add966abc30f6fda1261043593fb03bbe40bd7","tid":1261997,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:16:56.000Z","msg":"冇第三身 大把人唔買啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d65dee5e05c2573d35073bc317c30425c52b11e","tid":1261997,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5add966abc30f6fda1261043593fb03bbe40bd7","tid":1261997,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:16:56.000Z","msg":"冇第三身 大把人唔買啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:00:54.000Z","msg":"揸車果陣有"},{"pid":"4cae51151a56cb7b802595524e9b8421872555e0","tid":1261997,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d65dee5e05c2573d35073bc317c30425c52b11e","tid":1261997,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5add966abc30f6fda1261043593fb03bbe40bd7","tid":1261997,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:16:56.000Z","msg":"冇第三身 大把人唔買啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:00:54.000Z","msg":"揸車果陣有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}